generates bar codes for the Lego Code Pilot

based on information found under
http://www.elecbrick.com/lego/

just call the script with the code number as argument

./lego_code_pilot_barcodes.pl 0
# generates code0.png for turning on the motor

./lego_code_pilot_barcodes.pl 111
# generates code111.png for playing a C tone


by Matthias Wenzel under GPLv3
